rule_name: birds with (orange tails or white wings) and orange crests
text: The Luzak has orange hair, and a white arm. It can have a tail, and it is orange. It can have a white body or a purple body.

rule_name: birds with (orange tails or white wings) and orange crests
text: So the body is white or purple and the hair and tail are orange?

rule_name: birds with (orange tails or white wings) and orange crests
text: Yes that true, the arm has to be white for it to be a Luzak as well.

rule_name: birds with (orange tails or white wings) and orange crests

text: The species has to have pink fruits(they are circular). The stem and leaves can be of various colors, but the fruits are pink.
So anything with pink fruits is correct or is there another factor that would make pink fruits incorrect?
Anything that has pink fruits is correct, the stem and leaves vary.

rule_name: fish with orange bodies or fangs
text: If the fish has a tooth, it is always the species no matter the color. If it is toothless, the main body of the fish has to be orange.

rule_name: fish with orange bodies or fangs
text: So all fish that one tooth and all orange fish with no teeth?

rule_name: fish with orange bodies or fangs
text: Correct. One more thing, the toothless fish, the main body has to be orange, but it may have stripes that are white, purple, or even orange.

rule_name: fish with orange bodies or fangs
text: ...all fish that have one tooth....sorry for the typo. Got it.

rule_name: bugs with (purple legs and white heads) or orange wings
text: All insects with orange wings are the species. If it has white wings, it has to have a purple antenna, white head, purple legs, and orange body. If no wings, it has to have purple legs, can have no antenna or a white one, and the body varies. If purple wings, it has purple legs, orange antenna, and a white body and head.

rule_name: bugs with (purple legs and white heads) or orange wings
flowers with purple stem and thorns
text: All flowers with purple stems and spines are of the species. Both must be present. The other parts of the flower can be of different colors or be absent.

rule_name: flowers with purple stem and thorns
text: Awesome....so everything with purple stems and purple spines regardless of anything else?
